                "name": "Spider Empathy",
                "ability_type": "Extraordinary",
                "ability_type_abbrev": "Ex",
                "text": "This ability functions as the druid\u2019s wild empathy, save that an ettercap can only use this ability on spiders. An ettercap gains a +4 racial bonus on this check. Spiders are mindless, but this empathic communication imparts on them a modicum of implanted intelligence, allowing ettercaps to train giant spiders and use them as guardians."
